window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>A jaded single dad and a journalist with a doozy of a secret might be the perfect match to heal two broken hearts…or the perfect storm for disaster.</b></p> <p>Jazzy Simon used to be a pro at reading people. That is until she met Finn Walker, the broody musical genius behind the country’s hottest rock stars.</p> <p>As media correspondent for a new rock and roll documentary, Jazzy is there to get the paycheck her family desperately needs. For an added bonus payment, she'll expose a little scandal on the side.</p> <p>But as she spends more time with the guarded single dad whose dedication to his daughter lights her heart on fire, Jazzy’s ability to read people goes out the window, along with her suspicions that Finn is involved in anything more than school drop offs and ballet classes.</p> <p>When the sparks fly, secrets begin to fall apart, and hearts are put on the line. As the truth comes out, will they fight for a whirlwind romance, or will their love crash and burn?</p> <p>Perfect for those who love a good mix of sweet and sizzle, toe-curling kisses, swoony book boyfriends, and a happily ever after.</p>"; 
